<p>The  <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition-us-core-location.html">US Core Location profile</a>  <strong>SHALL</strong> be used to record location/facility-specific information.</p>

<p>The essential fields to be provided in the US Core Location resource are:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>R4 Hierarchical Name</th>
      <th>R4 Name</th>
      <th>Card.</th>
      <th>Type</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Location</td>
      <td>Location</td>
      <td>0..*</td>
      <td>Â </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Location.id</td>
      <td>id</td>
      <td>0..1</td>
      <td>id</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Location.status</td>
      <td>status</td>
      <td>0..1</td>
      <td>code</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Location.name</td>
      <td>name</td>
      <td>1..1</td>
      <td>string</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Location.telecom</td>
      <td>telecom</td>
