<h4 id="health-plan-mapping-assistance">Health Plan Mapping Assistance</h4>

<p>A collaboration of Health Plan experts have performed an evaluation of claims information and developed a mapping of data for Members to the <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition-us-core-location.html">US Core Location profile</a>. This is shown below as an assistance  to implementers:</p>

